DOCUMENT(); # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a1 = random(-400,400,10);
$b1 = random(-400,400,10);
$c1 = random(-400,400,10);
$d1 = random(-400,400,10);
$e1 = random(-400,400,10);
$pi = 3.1416;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
For each of the following angles, find the radian measure of the
angle with the given degree measure (you can enter \(\pi\) as
'pi' in your answers): $BR $BR \( $a1 \)
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT
$ans = $a1*$pi/180;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
\( $b1 \)
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT
$ans = $b1*$pi/180;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
\( $c1 \)
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT
$ans = $c1*$pi/180;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
\( $d1 \)
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT
$ans = $d1*$pi/180;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));
TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
\( $e1 \)
\{ans_rule(10) \}
$BR
EOT
$ans = $e1*$pi/180;
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

